{"tid":791183,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"高雄小琉球 五天四夜 廢噏之旅","createTime":"2018-08-23T14:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T18:28:06.000Z","uid":91858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2469fa0e42afa20481a15e886bb78a9ed6e28222","tid":791183,"uid":91858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"話說公司突然放我幾日假<br />\n所以由買機票到出發只係三日內既事<br />\n<br />\n其實本身諗住今次去峴港 <br />\n但係咁倉猝既決定 峴港賣剩既機票實在太貴 <br />\n最後決定用Asiamiles換高雄機票<br />\n<br />\n至於點解揀高雄 除左因為有機位之外<br />\n上一次獨遊係去台中清境阿里山<br />\n對於獨遊台灣既感覺都幾良好<br />\n所以就揀左高雄<br />\n<br />\n出發前都無乜時間plan行程 <br />\n剩係睇左天氣forecast <br />\n揀左一日天氣無咁差既book小琉球民宿<br />\n同埋求求其其睇過下高雄有咩景點<br />\n係咁架啦 獨遊 自由自在<br />\n<br />\n出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/224559_df7122fc3ddb4458b30dc2ee14eca123.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F224559_df7122fc3ddb4458b30dc2ee14eca123.png&h=53ab61d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f92fa0d824a1610dc3db16ad0e5332aa928cb6a","tid":791183,"uid":91858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"題外話講下<br />\n話說Asiamiles改左制<br />\n分左咩標準賞隨心賞之類 <br />\n又可以去程回程唔同class<br />\nd人話改完制換機票難左<br />\n<br />\n而我又咁岩去程無晒econ位<br />\n唯有局住嘔多幾千miles <br />\n去程坐business 回程坐econ<br />\n當體驗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n難得坐business <br />\n緊係狗衝下佢個lounge <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/230214_bce740accd0dc4c1c018d2f46282a2d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F230214_bce740accd0dc4c1c018d2f46282a2d1.png&h=31068865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似話香港機場好幾個cathay lounge<br />\n是但入左個 其實都係有個地方食d野坐下<br />\n野食都係果d大路野<br />\n係無諗過部咖啡機咁殘舊 都仲擺出黎<br />\n不過值得一讚既係<br />\n佢地茶包既brand都算幾Premium <br />\nJing Tea <br />\n都幾多五星級酒店用緊呢隻brand<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/230434_a0b98abc63db3979eaefb231d7c01d36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F230434_a0b98abc63db3979eaefb231d7c01d36.png&h=a66ec95d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/230435_2721af6f7171dc8778a3e2109671e90a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F230435_2721af6f7171dc8778a3e2109671e90a.png&h=457e7634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲左杯香檳 扮完有錢人 就拿拿臨趕番過去北衛星上飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/231956_7c98a73ff4b1b678b87a1504c47aacfb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F231956_7c98a73ff4b1b678b87a1504c47aacfb.png&h=5b076f68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2144d7c455bd9df442d14a149b45dafb52c3acf6","tid":791183,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"其實都幾悶下，小琉球係正，但啱情侶or一班人去。<br />\n高雄，除咗旗津，好似冇乜特別，壽山動物園睇孔雀ok。"},{"pid":"d12eec8ba208cf6036871ea0b1f36d31b0860883","tid":791183,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:12:47.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5aa8a1ba49d54ecbbe65cb9e7c373633702ffd4f","tid":791183,"uid":82078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"冇電單車牌去小琉球要租電動車好慘 成日唔夠力水上斜"},{"pid":"01b224dfbd216cab797110eea8af180e17029a88","tid":791183,"uid":79891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"高雄自己覺得幾舒服，冇乜人。可以去下義大樂園，啲VR幾好玩(不過自己去就難啲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。駁二藝術特區好多市集(最好假日去)。打狗英國領事館影下相。淨園農場有得餵動物。旗津睇風景，最好租單車，唔係行到腳斷。夜市就可以去六合同瑞豐。<br />\n富錦饗小籠包幾好食，又平又大粒。米糕城食魯肉飯。郭家肉粽啲粽好特別。丹丹漢堡都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小琉球就一定要潛水！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有得睇海龜"},{"pid":"d8650e55127c061c7045dc8aaa39b5923a4c33d0","tid":791183,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa8a1ba49d54ecbbe65cb9e7c373633702ffd4f","tid":791183,"uid":82078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"冇電單車牌去小琉球要租電動車好慘 成日唔夠力水上斜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"一個人都ok，係去燈塔果段好勉強，載埋人應該上唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe67f13db324050bcb06e08fcd2e3563d52d66e","tid":791183,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T22:24:53.000Z","msg":"高雄去一次就夠，好在有捷運"},{"pid":"c3988f4475649e601f62f407768ca6d771d2a85a","tid":791183,"uid":91858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:02:03.000Z","msg":"其實商務位都係多左杯welcome drink<br />\n坐位闊落d 同埋有得揀食咩飲咩<br />\n個零鐘機 食完野 𥄫下空姐 已經落機<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/082952_594d8b79d2f4e822e4e9ad55d7c1b72e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F082952_594d8b79d2f4e822e4e9ad55d7c1b72e.png&h=988b8846&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/082953_7aedc64573755bb89f432d45d0485d32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F082953_7aedc64573755bb89f432d45d0485d32.png&h=02e1f996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/083352_7b52140b73403b5796bc4d553c589943.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F083352_7b52140b73403b5796bc4d553c589943.png&h=9959c783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落機見到落晒雨咁 都擔心緊去小琉球會唔好天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/083353_a1381d8f5e1e7410e1c36acc9dc3c200.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F083353_a1381d8f5e1e7410e1c36acc9dc3c200.png&h=cdc5bcf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中午就落機 但係hostel四點先check-in<br />\n所以係機場搭一個站去左大魯閣草衙道<br />\n其實呢個集購物娛樂運動於一身既概念真係幾好 <br />\n星期日去都好熱鬧好多local<br />\n佢勝在入邊既設施唔同年齡層都岩玩 大路野有戲院 唱k 摩天輪 室內籃球場 機鋪 food court shopping 特別d既又有卡丁車 VR 棒球 如果一班人黎應該可以玩一日 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085426_06842cd3ce51839c464f51b9e2fb403c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085426_06842cd3ce51839c464f51b9e2fb403c.png&h=1aa3c8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085427_3a366925161d21b1907933ef481f24a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085427_3a366925161d21b1907933ef481f24a3.png&h=0d32cf03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085428_410c659b916f940ad5371b44963169a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085428_410c659b916f940ad5371b44963169a6.png&h=a3e2b49d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085429_cfdd8b91bff2f89aebe1cd26f226c8dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085429_cfdd8b91bff2f89aebe1cd26f226c8dc.png&h=3970b67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085848_da6eaa2d5fc1649d090eb92592d74c18.png\" data-