2cd3ce51839c464f51b9e2fb403c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085426_06842cd3ce51839c464f51b9e2fb403c.png&h=1aa3c8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085427_3a366925161d21b1907933ef481f24a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085427_3a366925161d21b1907933ef481f24a3.png&h=0d32cf03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085428_410c659b916f940ad5371b44963169a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085428_410c659b916f940ad5371b44963169a6.png&h=a3e2b49d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085429_cfdd8b91bff2f89aebe1cd26f226c8dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085429_cfdd8b91bff2f89aebe1cd26f226c8dc.png&h=3970b67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085848_da6eaa2d5fc1649d090eb92592d74c18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085848_da6eaa2d5fc1649d090eb92592d74c18.png&h=650b76cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個迷你golf場幾得意 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085624_c64d7fdcc64dfa62e565af0264ca37da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085624_c64d7fdcc64dfa62e565af0264ca37da.png&h=1957ea76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n棒球練習場 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085816_e95009056a486e368902c7b0ae0845e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085816_e95009056a486e368902c7b0ae0845e0.png&h=34d3b889&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/085817_288deb95c19a7d92111b237243216e92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F085817_288deb95c19a7d92111b237243216e92.png&h=aacc9659&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:32:23.000Z","msg":"上次星期一去，勁少人，好有以前愉景新城嘅感覺"},{"pid":"0c193051f45fc84d41a16c88be57ee23109cd97c","tid":791183,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:58:18.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"c2f92e48e50dceba4ee7f830e94b7bbc261419a9","tid":791183,"uid":714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"係咪好大雨 我過兩日去高雄 都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45e613ed90a5969af2ab745c2586aedbb88b7fa","tid":791183,"uid":141199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4cf583da9f883303fbbced88ddcbe08817dfb8be","tid":791183,"uid":91858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"係大魯閣hea行都行左3個鐘<br />\n如果多人一齊黎應該可以玩半日<br />\n<br />\n第一晚揀左間叫貝殻窩既hostel訓<br />\n係中央公園站行幾分鐘就到<br />\n一百蚊港紙晚 好抵住<br />\n又乾淨又方便仲送埋早餐<br />\n而且都幾多香港人住 <br />\n推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/230606_c658a580c24b34ea4ee3b92ee02fe65d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F230606_c658a580c24b34ea4ee3b92ee02fe65d.png&h=88eb738c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/230607_94283c485801e252606fd18868be3db0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F230607_94283c485801e252606fd18868be3db0.png&h=b90993e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無影到間房同個床位 上網搵左d圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/230740_7e7c2a26b0ec650a26210272dc4eb0cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F230740_7e7c2a26b0ec650a26210272dc4eb0cf.png&h=6f29125e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/230741_3f4be271d472a17fbb080993f4c4e854.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F230741_3f4be271d472a17fbb080993f4c4e854.png&h=8a914070&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/230743_b8a74d40c273b90153394ca319c3a019.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F230743_b8a74d40c273b90153394ca319c3a019.png&h=9e88584e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係hostel抖左陣就出發去青年夜市<br />\n青年夜市比起六合同瑞豐 多d local<br />\n唔會行幾步就聽到廣東話<br />\n不過就相對細d <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/231239_2529c4fc58cd67bc7648c47316880de2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F231239_2529c4fc58cd67bc7648c47316880de2.png&h=90739d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/231241_c5aa4c786b5c723b4fdbbf00ddc32ce1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F231241_c5aa4c786b5c723b4fdbbf00ddc32ce1.png&h=03e6eaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/231246_76bcf3f4f32fb05f1e4bf2f154f7f7fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F231246_76bcf3f4f32fb05f1e4bf2f154f7f7fc.png&h=2818fefb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/231247_085efc16b54aa6653d7ce05e91a9b12e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F231247_085efc16b54aa6653d7ce05e91a9b12e.png&h=c854ffac&s